{"word":"στοναχή","slug":"στοναχή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>στοναχή</b></el> <el>(στονᾰχή, ἡ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:στενάχω'><el>στενάχω</el></a>\n<p/><i>a groaning, wailing</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; in <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> <i>groans, sighs</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/>"}]}